blog.description:
AL, 27, Queer Panda in England. Disney fan since my birth to my death.
Fandoms: Recently: KILLING EVE! Captain Marvel and Brie Larson! Star Wars: Reylo! | Jessica Jones| OITNB| Greys | GoT | | Orphan black | Fruits basket and so many to come... Has a side blog for Duggars and fundies: savescience-eatfundies

body:
So shocked at the moment!

My straight friend did not find Killing Eve that good. And she thinks that “the blond one” is not that good of an actress.

She really does not get the point! And who can say Jodie Comer is not that great…. She is so amazing! 😍 I am starting to be worry for my friend, she does not know what’s good and her opinion doesn’t count for me anymore. I need to have more queer friends at work to discuss that…

blog.name: jamesphillimoresumbrella
blog.title: Think of me with my nose in a book!
blog.description:
Much too cold. Nasty Woman. A hodgepodge of stuff, starting with Sherlock going through Pratchett and Gaiman all the way to Marvel and Star Wars, and all points in between. Um. It really is the fangirling you should be afraid of. Everything else is transport.

"Among these unfinished tales is that of Mr. James Phillimore, who, stepping back into his own house to get his umbrella, was never more seen in this world." - Sir Arthur Conan Doyle, The Problem of Thor Bridge "We can confirm that this apparent suicide closely resembles those of Sir Jeffrey Patterson and James Phillimore. In the light of this these incidents are being treated as linked. The investigation is ongoing but Detective Inspector Lestrade will take questions now." - Sgt. Sally Donovan, A Study in Pink

My fic on AO3 (I write as tepidspongebath).
